.TH "_base_readl_aero" 9 "_base_readl_aero" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
_base_readl_aero \- retry readl for max three times.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "u32" _base_readl_aero
.BI "(const volatile void __iomem *addr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "addr" 12
MPT Fusion system interface register address
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Retry the \fBreadl\fP for max three times if it gets zero value
while reading the system interface register.
